  quote: 'Yogi Johnson stood looking out of the window of a big pump-factory in Michigan. Spring would soon be here. Could it be that what this writing fellow Hutchinson had said, \'If winter comes, can spring be far behind?\' would be true again this year? Yogi Johnson wondered.'
